name: Just Tuk’n Around – Progressive Dinner
description: Experience Airlie Beach like a local on a fun and flavour-filled Progressive Dinner Tuk Tuk Tour. This unique evening experience combines great food, local favourites and a scenic ride aboard an eco-friendly tuk tuk — the perfect way to dine and explore without the hassle of driving or parking.
highlights: Three-Course Progressive Dinner | Perfect for Groups & Couples | No Driving or Parking Hassles | Local Guided Insight & Hidden Gems | Local Food | Eco-Friendly Tuk Tuk Transport
includes: 2/3 Seater Tuk Tuk | Entrée, Main, Dessert and 1 cocktail | Guide
ideal_for: Couples | Friends | Celebrations | Anyone looking for a memorable night out
itinerary: Loads of Tuk Tuk fun and local information with a wonderful 3 course dinner and cocktail included at 3 different mystery restaurants.
important_info: Meet outside Tree House Cafe- next to the Lagoon 15 mins prior to departure time. Cameras and a bottle of water are recommended.
tags: Airlie Beach, progressive dinner, tuk tuk, local food, eco-friendly

name: Just Tuk’n Around – Guided Tours
description: Discover Airlie Beach in a fun, relaxed and uniquely local way with Just Tuk’n Around. Cruise along scenic coastal roads and hidden backstreets aboard an eco-friendly tuk tuk, guided by friendly locals who know Airlie Beach inside and out.
highlights: Fun Tuk Tuk Tours in Airlie Beach | Multiple Tour Options Available | Progressive Dinner & Sunset Tours | Local Guided Insight & Hidden Gems | Perfect for All Groups | Relaxing, Scenic Coastal Route
departure_times: Check - 15 mins prior to departure time
ideal_for: Couples | Families | Groups | Cruise Ship Visitors
itinerary: Sit back, relax and take in the spectacular scenery as we buzz you along the footpaths and boardwalks of Airlie Beach, the heart of the tropical Whitsundays.
important_info: Meet outside Tree House Cafe- next to the Lagoon 15 mins prior to departure time. Please note: All bookings are subject to availability.
tags: tuk tuk, guided tours, Airlie Beach, scenic tours
